{
  "stem": "19969.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 226.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The, the only major battle we had after the Rhine River was at a city called Aschaffenburg, Germany, which was on the Main River, which, is a tributary of the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there, we run into a fanatical group of Germans who were defending the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it took us a week to clear the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we took some pretty heavy casualties, but nothing like the Germans did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took probably 5,000 casualties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had-- in my battalion, I had about 200.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then my battalion and, and the other two battalions of the regiment cleared Aschaffenburg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it took us a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, as I say, it was hard fighting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Village or town fighting is always difficult because it's very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You see, you, you go around the corner, and you're you're getting shot at from a window or a cellar, basement.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So the fighting is very close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It means that when you get hit, you get hit at very close range.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's the case where most of the wounds are caused by rifles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You can't use artillery to amount to anything in a-- in a city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's almost-- artillery is almost useless if you're actually fighting in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So you have to do it by hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's a hand operation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That means grenades and rifles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was pretty costly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But there was a German garrison of about 5,000 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And with less than that, we overcame it and-- in a week's time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "From there on, then, we moved fairly rapidly towards Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the Germans then made another stand at Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "See, all this time, I am a lieutenant colonel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I'm a battalion commander at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "In Nuremberg, we have some tough resistance for, like, one day.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
